The most popular and used commands

cd Desktop/NameYourApp - the root directory of your app

ls // show all files your app

ls -a // show all files of your application together with hidden

git add .
git commit -m "My message"

git add --all

git fetch // get all changes

git log  // Show all commits

git branch // Show all branches and current branch

git branch newBranchName // Create new branch with name newBranchName

git checkout -b newBranchName // Create and go to new branch with name newBranchName

git checkout newBranchName // Go to the branch newBranchName

git merge newBranchName // Необходимо сидеть на другой ветке (например develop), код берем с ветки newBranchName

git status // show files whos dont commited


--------
How to clone and download project from git with the help terminal?

1. cd Desctop/
2. git clone "link to the project from git, without brackets"

